CrossReferenceVendor is a BusinessClass
    owned by ap
    prefix is AXV
    classic name is APPOVNXREF

    Ontology
        symbolic key is CrossReferenceVendor
            classic set name is AXVSET1
            classic name is XREF-VENDOR

    Patterns
        implements StaticJava
        disable AuditIndex

    Persistent Fields

        Description
            classic name is XREF-VEN-DESC
        Buyer
            classic name is BUYER-CODE

    Sets

        Set2
            indexed
            Sort Order
                VendorGroup
                CrossReferenceVendor
				Vendor

	Relations
		VendorCrossReferencesRel
			one-to-many relation to CrossReferenceVendor
			Field Mapping uses symbolic key
				related.VendorGroup = VendorGroup
				related.Vendor		= Vendor
			Instance Selection
				where (related.CrossReferenceVendor	!= CrossReferenceVendor)
			

	Actions
		Create is a Create Action
			Action Rules
				invoke Update Vendor
					invoked.CrossReferenceExists = true

		Update is an Update Action

		Delete is a Delete Action
			Entrance Rules
				invoke Update Vendor
					if (VendorCrossReferencesRel exist)
						invoked.CrossReferenceExists = true
					else
						invoked.CrossReferenceExists = false

		Purge is a Purge Action
			restricted
